      <title>Altice International 因实验室和外汇问题下调盈利前景</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-27/altice-international-lowers-earnings-outlook-on-labs-fx-woes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于帕特里克·德拉希 (Patrick Drahi) 陷入困境的电信帝国的部分业务持续恶化，Altice International 下调了今年的盈利预期。]]></description>
