      <title>电池制造商 Morrow 呼吁明确关键贷款</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-27/battery-maker-morrow-calls-norway-to-rule-on-make-or-break-loan</link>
      <description><![CDATA[挪威的 Morrow Batteries AS 正面临生存危机，该公司正在等待政府资金批准，而这项资金对于吸引投资者进入因瑞典初创公司 Northvolt AB 倒闭而受到重创的行业至关重要。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-27/battery-maker-morrow-calls-norway-to-rule-on-make-or-break-loan</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 27 Nov 2024 12:57:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Brookfield 放弃以 68 亿美元收购制药商 Grifols 的提议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-27/brookfield-drops-6-8-billion-offer-to-buy-drugmaker-grifols</link>
      <description><![CDATA[布鲁克菲尔德资产管理有限公司 (Brookfield Asset Management Ltd.) 放弃了收购 Grifols SA 的计划，结束了为期数月的收购这家西班牙血浆公司的谈判。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-27/brookfield-drops-6-8-billion-offer-to-buy-drugmaker-grifols</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 27 Nov 2024 12:57:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>OPEC 的困境：又一年的供应限制或油价暴跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-27/opec-s-dilemma-another-year-of-oil-supply-curbs-or-price-slump</link>
      <description><![CDATA[当 OPEC+ 部长本周末开会时，他们将面临一个难以接受的选择：继续限制石油供应直至 2025 年，否则将面临油价再度暴跌的风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-27/opec-s-dilemma-another-year-of-oil-supply-curbs-or-price-slump</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 27 Nov 2024 09:17:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>交易商等待 OPEC+ 生产计划线索，油价小幅上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-26/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-november-27</link>
      <description><![CDATA[有迹象表明 OPEC+ 将再次推迟恢复产量，抵消了中东地缘政治风险的缓解，油价小幅走高。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-26/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-november-27</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 26 Nov 2024 23:36:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
